Chloe Hor studied English with Creative Writing at UNM. At UNM, she was an editor for the literary magazine Particle, a Junior Writer for Ignite, and a writer for DAG magazine. The Nottingham Alumni Awards presents you with an opportunity to nominate yourself or other deserving alumni in five different categories, highlighting your achievements and recognising how far you have progressed in your career after graduation.
